## What kind of events can you receive

GOB>UK Signals exchange platform uses [Shared Signals Events Framework](https://openid.net/specs/openid-sse-framework-1_0.html) (SSE) to send user related activity. Events that are supported by GOV.UK One Login are

* Specific to users interacting with GOV.UK One Login with your service
* Events related to the user but not to an interaction with your service.


